data.description: Spacious four-bedroom home in sought-after Grand Prairie subdivision and Plainfield 202 school district! Open concept eat-in kitchen with updated cabinets and newer stainless steel appliances, plus a separate dining room with a sliding door out to the deck. Main level also boasts vaulted ceilings over the living and dining room, and three bedrooms including a huge master bedroom with vaulted ceiling and shared master bathroom with double sinks. Lower level has fourth bedroom, second full bathroom, laundry room, and family room with sliding glass door leading to the patio. The back yard is amazing and perfect for entertaining, with an upper-level deck, 20'x 10' brick paver patio with brick fire pit, storage shed, and newer vinyl fence. Low-maintenance exterior with 5-year old roof, and vinyl siding. Attached extra-deep 2.5 car garage fits all of your storage needs. Convenient location is a short walk to Grand Prairie Tot Park and Woodside Park, just 3 minutes to Grand Prairie Elementary, 5 minutes to Timber Ridge Middle School, 10 minutes to Plainfield Central; easy commuting at 3 minutes to I-55 via Rt 30. Plenty of shopping and restaurants at nearby Louis Joliet Mall. Sold as-is though it's in fantastic shape.
